[src:threejs/webglrenderingcontext] Sets the line width of rasterized lines.
[src:threejs/webglrenderingcontext] Specifies the scale factors and units to calculate depth values.
[src:threejs/webglrenderingcontext] Specifies multi-sample coverage parameters for anti-aliasing effects.
[src:threejs/webglrenderingcontext] Sets the both front and back function and reference value for stencil testing.
[src:threejs/webglrenderingcontext] Sets the front and/or back function and reference value for stencil testing.
[src:threejs/webglrenderingcontext] Controls enabling and disabling of both the front and back writing of individual bits in the stencil planes.
[src:threejs/webglrenderingcontext] Controls enabling and disabling of front and/or back writing of individual bits in the stencil planes.
[src:threejs/webglrenderingcontext] Sets both the front and back-facing stencil test actions.
[src:threejs/webglrenderingcontext] Sets the front and/or back-facing stencil test actions.
